      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IM FRANKEE (6) started a hot favourite on debut and overcame a poor start to to score by 3.8m at Menangle. Draws wider but has been back to the trials so should have come on and looks to have plenty of upside. BUMPER CROP (1) looks promising having come from a wider barrier to kick off his career with a 2.6m win at Terang. Should be better for that and the ace draw gives him the chance to strike again.  KYVALLEY DIXON (4) is at the track for the first time. By Majestic Son and hails from the Brent Lilley stable. Looked above average in winning the latest trial at Kilmore so can make an immediate impact. Elite Stride filly HALFYOURSHALFMINE (5) debuts after placing in her last two trials in Victoria. Market watch.",
